{
  "stem": "13258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no organization set up at that point, unless you could get to Kuybyshev, a city on the Volga, where the Polish govern-- where the Russian government had been evacuated from Moscow, and where the Polish Embassy was.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was difficult to get there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got into a place called Asbest, A-S-B-E-S-T.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's the center of the Soviet Russian asbestos industry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is about two hours by train from what the city, which we call-- was called Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's now back Yekaterinburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's the place where the last Czar was murdered by the soviets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got into Asbest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By misinformation, I thought I was going to be able to get a job in the ceramics industry, which wasn't so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We worked all kinds of jobs over there, building trades and that, shoveling snow around the factory, and as a mechanic's apprentice, setting up punch presses and doing all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was also working there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was really the worst place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And twice from there, we were sent to farms, in summer once, and once in fall, to help with the harvest, which was good, because at least there, we had enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "While we were in the city for a long time, we were starving, until, for the first time, help came from the American Poles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There came food supplies, and there came clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The clothing mostly had come from England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think the food supplies, a lot of it, had come from England, but, but most, some of it from America.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a big colony of Poles and Jews from Poland there, and luckily, the Poles had elected a physician, a Dr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Mark ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
